// Original Name: Level 3 Intro
:: Level3Intro
Email Notification:
{@article} El, we've been keeping up with your work in Twin Lakes!
{@article} Very impressive. There might be a place for you at the Smoke City Herald after all.
{@article} If you're interested, have your editor send over a letter of recommendation. 
{@article} -Gabby White, Senior Editor, Smoke City Herald 
{clear-text}
